Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是模拟弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到警告音响起还有谁能冷静下来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.93,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,J1，你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心跳停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生紧急状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,J1驾驶员似乎因为某种原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在驾驶舱内死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前由辅助AI控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切换到自动驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.65,0:04:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飞行状态安定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坠落的危险性为零
