Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除指令I.S
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻回航本舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通告所有部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生紧急状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,J1驾驶员似乎因为某种原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在直升机内死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.74,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除指令I.S
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依据指令S.A采取避难行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重复一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.61,0:05:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依据指令S.A采取避难行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.55,0:05:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HA-01AV没有解除指令I.S
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶员的生命维持反应到现在仍全部正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然确认心跳已经停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于电子脑仍在发出生存信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以AI无视管制中心的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决定优先保护驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并将避难行动解释为外来攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，细腰蜂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久保田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来事态紧急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要那里有犯罪的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.87,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就会忍不住插手是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.62,0:06:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然目前告诉媒体说是实验机种的空中加油训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但事实上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是政府为了配合最近即将实施的难民政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.53,0:06:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近三年来最大规模同时也是在极机密状态下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所举行的实弹演习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出问题的直升机不是那架与美帝间的安保条约有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因涉嫌不法勾结而谣言四起的思考直升机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并不是那一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陆自也害怕被媒体攻击(陆自，陆上自卫军的简称）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.28,0:07:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以派出利用现有机体改良的AI辅助型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.48,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,俗称“细腰蜂ADVANCE”的机种来参与演习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事件的起因则始终认定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.02,0:07:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于驾驶员意外死亡所引发的一连串事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.23,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这个事态发展也太可疑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是瞒不过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.47,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你那边掌握到什么程度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实弹演习时辅助型反战车直升机的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在演习中倒下是上午5时57分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.58,0:07:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来在辅助AI的自动驾驶之下似乎已经平安无事的直升机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却无视于管制中心的解除命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.52,0:07:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在6时3分朝招慰难民居住区上空飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且在这之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.39,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辅助AI同时侵入航空母舰上的两架同型机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及一架空中加油机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.80,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,共计三架于6时12分飞离航空母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.11,0:08:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各机在难民居住区上空会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.94,0:08:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,据说目前仍在电波发射塔上面盘旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大致上都是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外，有未确认的情报显示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,淡路驻地有2架和歌山驻地有3架同型直升机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.05,0:08:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被辅助AI以联机诱导方式在无人的状况下飞走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到联络的各基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.36,0:08:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然立刻将同型机的AI切换为自闭模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是处理慢半拍的伊丹基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.57,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有两架跟在后面飞走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是以辅助AI为目标的计算机恐怖活动吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.68,0:08:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突破军方的防壁吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情报部也发现到有恐怖活动的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.45,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经拘留辅助AI的全体开发人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且进行各项调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却什么都没有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.53,0:09:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是军队内部反弹引发的武装叛变吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.63,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是受个别主义者的影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我甚至怀疑过是不是那些加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.67,0:09:15.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,圣母悼歌：Stabat Mater 自称千禧年的某艺术家制作并发起的CyberDome Game\N通过向全体观众电子脑内移入软件程序产生互动性影像空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.67,0:09:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前成为媒体抨击目标的“圣母悼歌”享乐集团的队员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.01,0:09:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所犯下的罪行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是那个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在上面正在拼命想办法用意外事故这个理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把事情解决掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.89,0:09:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所幸攻击直升机只在电波发射塔上空盘旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.89,0:09:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是能这样解决就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民...吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是这样，少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我们掌握到的情报差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.64,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，现场好象在县警机动队控制之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是逐渐开始骚动的难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.05,0:09:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就连前来收拾局面的陆自机动部队也被挡在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.29,0:10:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,县警就像是挺身出来主张难民居住区由自己管辖一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是难看死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直无药可救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.76,0:10:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然先派托古萨和石川去调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在飞行中死亡的那位驾驶员的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我们该怎么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就要到达难民居住区了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠近现场后先待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事我们要不要出面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须等总理最后的判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.58,0:10:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚刚说的不可以泄漏出去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是被人看到我跟你坐在这里就会很麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还抛不掉升官的愿望吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.36,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉，我没办法像你那样过生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.10,0:10:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是公安9课的荒卷先生吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.44,0:11:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内阁情报厅战略影响调查会议代表辅佐官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田一人..(Hitori)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田一人(Kazundo，同字不同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.42,0:11:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很少遇到有人能念对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.86,0:11:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我不觉得这个名字很特殊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，现在我开始觉得这是一个很好的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为只要说一次对方往往都能记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特别是跟这张脸一起说的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.77,0:11:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么内阁情报厅找我有何贵干?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.11,0:11:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于现在发生的这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.98,0:11:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们想请你们公安9课协助解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.45,0:11:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然知道这样很失礼但还是直接来拜访您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想您应该知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们内阁情报厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,位于官房长官之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一个以收集、分析国内外情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且偶尔做点舆论操纵工作为主要活动的机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.97,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望您能将这次的事当作官房长官亲自下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟以首相的危机管理能力来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.85,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无法期待她能够当机立断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.25,0:12:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个有多大的供油能力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果规格和以前一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汽车可以连续开六年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使吃油超凶的细腰蜂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.36,0:12:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里面装载的燃料应该也够让它连续飞行10个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.40,0:13:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，像那样分给全部机体的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,单纯数字上的计算每一架应该还能飞1小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.41,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以细腰蜂通常续航时间为2.5小时来计算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.84,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们还能飞行的极限应该已经不到1个小时了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.32,0:13:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个油桶有没有可能先掉下来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大甲虫会最后才掉下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.36,0:13:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为它自己会越来越轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,续航时间也会延长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生，我问你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些家伙和我们一样都是AI对不对?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.10,0:13:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛，听说充其量只是以有人驾驶为前提的辅助型AI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话虽然这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.21,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然现在没人在上面它应该算是靠自己思考在飞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.35,0:13:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们真的非常不喜欢现有的工作条件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.65,0:13:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军队的工作条件那么差吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个性灰暗的AI真的很容易抓狂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.29,0:14:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我们还是得依照命令跟它们作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.03,0:14:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反战车直升机应该算是我们的天敌吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生，巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.34,0:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们肚子痛，可以先回去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.24,0:14:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们的肚子在哪里啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.09,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陆自那些家伙靠太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想潜入辅助AI结果失败了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陆自驾驶员的薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好象真的很低呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事情了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然特地跑到现场来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.15,0:15:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也就是说总理手上的缰绳还没松开?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，我先跟你说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是内阁情报厅的官员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战略影响调查会议的合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先说结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.03,0:15:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从现在起为了解决本次事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.17,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现场指挥权全面移交给我们公安9课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过这次作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.14,0:15:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你们完全依照他拟定的方法执行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.48,0:15:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爹，你疯了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.45,0:16:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们留在9课可不是为了当政府养的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据我们的计算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.75,0:16:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,48分钟后第一架直升机就会坠毁在难民居住区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了那个地步事情将无可挽回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.46,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这很明显已经是恐怖活动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就听听你的作战计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高兴你诚实面对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.18,0:16:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你完全相信那家伙说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是为何答应他的要求?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.25,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶员暴毙和AI的失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算与恐怖活动无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是直升机如果坠毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必然会给这一带造成一定的损害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.99,0:16:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那时候难民的动向很难说不会变成危险的火药库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.56,0:16:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何况没有那家伙给的情报我们原本就没有解决方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.10,0:16:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想说的是我们的立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，不说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斋藤，准备好了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.16,0:17:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是会动的东西不管是什么都加以攻击吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以下到地面上喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被空对地飞弹锁定就逃不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形势不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但二对一 而且火力原本就比不上它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，跟那家伙说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特，目标机体跟过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已确认目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.84,0:19:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，通过正面的时候请让目标稍微抬起下巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了不破坏AI而只击中驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想从驾驶座挡风玻璃侧面贯穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.65,0:19:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受管制中心发出的作战指令解除命令了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.44,0:20:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,预测没有出错真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.28,0:21:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要切断心脏停止的驾驶员电子脑所发出的讯号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.22,0:21:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辅助AI应该就会接受管制中心发出的作战指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.12,0:21:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我委托你们处理本案的眼光也非常正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.76,0:21:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多亏了你们，让自卫官们不必背负杀害同僚的污名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.27,0:21:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我们9课的斋藤背负污名就没关系罗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特，我早就习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.58,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚已经确认11架全部返航了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听过托古萨的报告了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.09,0:21:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那个驾驶员的家里发现了心脏病的药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.06,0:21:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他似乎对长官隐瞒了病情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.40,0:21:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么少校，你是认为这件事并非他说的恐怖活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.57,0:22:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充其量只是意外?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.27,0:22:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果没有将找到的药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.41,0:22:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟暴毙驾驶员的血液做成分分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本没有办法确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.02,0:22:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内阁情报厅出现的时机仿佛他们早就知道一切真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.49,0:22:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有只是恶作剧般地挑起难民的反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.43,0:22:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着摆出一副那就是真正目的的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从他们头上飞走的陆自直升机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.60,0:22:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这到底意味着什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定在我们不知道的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.01,0:22:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一桩大型的犯罪已经开始萌芽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.58,0:23:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.28,0:23:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.76,0:23:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.79,0:23:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.06,0:23:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.57,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.67,0:23:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字——然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.21,0:23:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省视自身——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.48,0:23:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我——时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.61,0:23:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相，所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.02,0:23:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去让这一切成真的——它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.99,0:24:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在躯壳里的美丽
